of Indian Film Directors Association, associated as Member with Film Writers Association, Indian Motion Pictures Producers Association.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2019/aug/04/yesteryear-bollywood-actor-chandrashekhar-vaidya-is-97-years-young-2014028.html|title=Yesteryear Bollywood actor Chandrashekhar Vaidya is 97 years young!|website=The New Indian Express|accessdate=8 April 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806130911/http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/2019/aug/04/yesteryear-bollywood-actor-chandrashekhar-vaidya-is-97-years-young-2014028.html|archive-date=6 August 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nChandrashekhar retired from the industry in 2000 after appearing in ''[[Khauff]]'' at the age of 78.\n\nChandrashekhar's son Ashok Shekhar is a known television serial producer and also runs an events and celeb management company, and his grandson [[Shakti Arora]], is an actor.<ref>{{cite news|author=Neha Maheshwri, TNN|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-04-19/tv/31367302_1_shakti-arora-chandrashekhar-hindi-and-urdu|title=Shakti Arora is Chandrashekhar's grandson|publisher=The Times of India|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2013-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204022726/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-04-19/tv/31367302_1_shakti-arora-chandrashekhar-hindi-and-urdu|archive-date=4 December 2012|url-status=live}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/silsila-badalte-rishton-kas-shakti-arora-shares-a-picture-with-96-year-old-grandfather-and-veteran-actor-chandrashekhar/articleshow/69436455.cms|title=Silsila Badalte Rishton Ka's Shakti Arora shares a picture with 96-year-old grandfather and veteran actor Chandrashekhar - Times of India|website=The Times of India|accessdate=8 April 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522234422/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/silsila-badalte-rishton-kas-sh